"A.P.238/4/8":
"Hey, partner.
How you doing progressing towards your goal?
I'm not doing well at all."

"Well, randomly searching for someone
is like that, though,
so there's no need to worry about it."

"Oh yeah, you know about the Battle-Skills Tournament?
Are you planning on participating in it?"

"Part of me feels like it isn't the time to do
something like that... But it could also
be the perfect time for a break."

"Way things are going, I'm just about at my limit
Hmm...if you're going to participate, partner,
I think I might too."

"I might have some sort of
breakthrough because of it...
Alright, yeah, I'm going to participate."

"Oh, of course,
if that's is fine with you, partner?"

"According to the rules,
you have to pair up with someone."

"Hehe, see you later!
Feel free to invite me to join you on the day of the tournament!"

"よっ、相棒。
そっちの目的の首尾はどうよ。
おれの方はさっぱり。"

"ま、あてもない人探しなんて
こんなもんだから
気にしてもいらんないけどな。"

"そういや、今度やる戦技大会っての？
あれ、お前も参加するのか？"

"そんなことやってる場合じゃない気も
するけど……まあ、気分転換には
ちょうどいいのかもな。"

"かくいうおれも行き詰まってるわけだし
うーん……相棒が参加するなら
おれも参加してみようかな。"

"何かブレイクスルー的なことが
あるかもしれないし……
よし、そうだ、そうしよう。"

"あ、もちろん、
相棒がよければ、だぜ？"

"ルール的に誰かと組まなきゃ
いけないらしいからよ。"

"へへっ、んじゃな！
当日、よかったら誘ってくれよ！"
